race.comment: ALLEGEDLY (1) is going better than it looks. Placed this course and distance two back then solid in richer company in town last time. Great record this circuit and expected to go close. BALISTIQUE (5) wasn't disgraced in town two back then well off best in tougher latest. Worth noting both career wins have been here so looks an improver. NIGHT CRUISER (8) was strongly fancied over 1800m at Clare and after racing on pace dropped out in a disappointing run. Change of rider and back in trip is worth another chance. RUADA (3) was also poor over further last time but has won this shorter journey and with good early speed will give a sight. DODD (4) has been thereabouts lately and did win only try this circuit. Low draw and gets chance to find form.
